# Git identity and attribution

All commits in this repo must be authored by **Dmitri Toren** `<52277457+mitya-toren@users.noreply.github.com>`.

When creating commits:
- Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor`, `Made-with: Cursor`, or any Cursor/agent attribution trailer.
- Never use `git commit --trailer` for Cursor attribution.
- Use plain `git commit -m "..."` (or `-F`) with subject/body only.
- If a trailer was added by the environment, amend the commit to remove it before pushing.
